{"tid":2311366,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"給肥佬黎的信  #政事","createTime":"2020-12-04T04:17:03.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-21T14:53:58.000Z","uid":25558,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"dcc2f9efda6e6f22547afcabec51a9ec2dea5782","tid":2311366,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-04T04:17:03.000Z","msg":"給肥佬黎的信 <br />\n#政事<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DHYzuyo.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDHYzuyo.jpg&h=12d16d5b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201204/5QR3VVWPRFH2HBVZFIJVLHZBNA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201204%2F5QR3VVWPRFH2HBVZFIJVLHZBNA%2F&d=my%2BdBOIpGqNKE9iEaZHJGNWqQ%2Br5Wu6dnGlIIIMUdw0%3D&h=6b05518e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201204%2F5QR3VVWPRFH2HBVZFIJVLHZBNA%2F&h=cdb26487\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201204/5QR3VVWPRFH2HBVZFIJVLHZBNA/</a><br />\n<br />\n給肥佬黎的信<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/F1FJX6PxlrWe5CYaXBRhIroRtxo=/5862x3918/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/JFUZ64P7L5F6HKUHRCXNKFGKPI.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FF1FJX6PxlrWe5CYaXBRhIroRtxo%3D%2F5862x3918%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FJFUZ64P7L5F6HKUHRCXNKFGKPI.jpg&h=dd38f6bf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n黎智英<br />\n<br />\n黎智英還柙期間，除了跟律師會面商討案件，每天只獲安排一名親友探望。他最喜愛的手機已被沒收，失去跟世界的大部份聯繫。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：大狀：保釋是人權 還柙須理由充份  未審先囚 多案違法律原則<br />\n<br />\n然而，收押所內肥佬黎每天仍可閱報，包括《蘋果日報》。若讀者們想為他加油打氣，不妨給他寫信，我們收到來信後，會把你們的心意刊登在《蘋果日報》，讓失去自由的黎智英能感受外界對他的支持。<br />\n<br />\n謝謝各位！<br />\n<br />\n（來信可寄將軍澳工業邨駿盈街八號一樓《蘋果日報》，或email至adnews@appledaily.com）"},{"pid":"2e5c5ebd765833e1d2cbd2032d6bcf604b63953f","tid":2311366,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-04T05:53:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ab9e140973ef4d3b505220417ef1ab3476b9faa","tid":2311366,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-04T07:15:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"46419924e0adbcde5fbb785d5b72125c7637f2b1","tid":2311366,"uid":21757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-04T10:30:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd9c0deb9cd6f3c9dbc1055c8640996f77a01929","tid":2311366,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-04T13:16:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab4e36a423f959dea44eb300007886996fec2ed6","tid":2311366,"uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-05T01:43:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pQFijgU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpQFijgU.jpg&h=7c0bd6b2&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1621f2d8381fd8c108dfba04d71760b388d984c4","tid":2311366,"uid":91236,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-05T02:11:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf503e5df81a05be3a721aff2776a56dc2645d87","tid":2311366,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-05T04:56:39.000Z","msg":"點解《蘋果日報》唔敢報道《壹週刊》偽造訪問害我？"},{"pid":"4cec0b1ea53e3f571425437f560ee560b38e6859","tid":2311366,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-06T03:37:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gVKWez5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgVKWez5.jpg&h=9adb79a2&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"43fc671cbbc68363fe3e5ce5946ef9c4b7468d88","tid":2311366,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-07T02:56:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pvtTpzH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpvtTpzH.jpg&h=2357a562&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"122ac4e3ed686ca396a035115721d03ca3a07231","tid":2311366,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-08T02:29:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ndfR3xg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FndfR3xg.jpg&h=299e82e0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e52184d6b9eb6784e8f7eb1737dbb8c7848b050a","tid":2311366,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-09T07:15:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Kw7EAYH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKw7EAYH.jpg&h=0ee72ad5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4bb615f0a78966fb9f1219c75ab092f658d1d4e9","tid":2311366,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-09T09:24:24.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201209/V6GY7MF655HR7DDWBWG6YT76AE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201209%2FV6GY7MF655HR7DDWBWG6YT76AE%2F&d=my%2BdBOIpGqNKE9iEaZHJGNWqQ%2Br5Wu6dnGlIIIMUdw0%3D&h=6f5e8bf3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201209%2FV6GY7MF655HR7DDWBWG6YT76AE%2F&h=fa7b1bc0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201209/V6GY7MF655HR7DDWBWG6YT76AE/</a><br />\n<br />\n你的堅持 我畢生受用<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/_lqC29hwT1Mv_hv3e57Phw0sqFY=/1772x1772/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/FJDRLFE5SZFS3M7KBZONVGMXHQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F_lqC29hwT1Mv_hv3e57Phw0sqFY%3D%2F1772x1772%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FFJDRLFE5SZFS3M7KBZONVGMXHQ.jpg&h=14a205de&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■有《蘋果日報》員工依創刊電視廣告繪圖，盼黎智英仍像25年前般，&ldquo;No fear we have to fight on.&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n黎智英昨天在收押所度過73歲生日，也是他被關押的第六天。連日來香港人送上的祝福從無間斷，有掛念他的手足、有嚮往公平公義的年輕人，也有同業的共勉。有讀者更打趣叫「肥佬黎」在收押所化身「記者」發掘「猛料」。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：「佢唔諗自己，只睇點樣幫大家」<br />\n<br />\n祝福以外，更多人感謝黎智英以生命影響生命。有讀者從《蘋果日報》、《壹週刊》中學懂反思，分辨是非；有年輕人牢記黎智英說過不移民、不離開，也決心留在香港。有海外留學生從沒忘記黎智英在香港最艱難時刻的堅持，「對我來說是畢生受用」。<br />\n<br />\n每一封寄給黎智英的信，都在訴說一個故事。有大學生說，小時候父親每天都買《蘋果日報》，一買就多年，去年更與父親一起訂閱蘋果，「自由有價，自然新聞也應有價」。他說一直都希望為香港做些事，但在今日香港，會思考自己的付出是否值得，「在極度壓迫的環境下為求生存而放棄的是否值得」。<br />\n<br />\n當眼見很多同學朋友都移民外地，他卻記得黎智英在訪問中說過不移民、不離開，不久前他便決心留在香港，「黎先生，蘋果在香港人爭取民主、自由與真相的道路上從沒缺席。而你本人也對香港不離不棄。自然，當您身受牢獄之災時，港人也必定不會放棄您、放棄自己、放棄香港，如此黎先生也可放心。希望上主憐恤眾人，保守您和其他入獄手足的身體健康。願能早日相見」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/QgSSzX3NaPKBpQ4732h8JG_UmVw=/777x904/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/CLM5UL6UWBCCNOSVC2AJGTXCPE.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FQgSSzX3NaPKBpQ4732h8JG_UmVw%3D%2F777x904%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FCLM5UL6UWBCCNOSVC2AJGTXCPE.gif&h=36ccb19f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n一如既往 不會屈服<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/WzongeTlyxjRtHmGJpYvLnr_bws=/606x507/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/SJNTHI5Q2BBDFGBMNB4FIBPLIM.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FWzongeTlyxjRtHmGJpYvLnr_bws%3D%2F606x507%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FSJNTHI5Q2BBDFGBMNB4FIBPLIM.gif&h=e197a0a8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nProud of you, as always<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/2sBsHtiJ2LSLt1V0WCV4ILwOmi0=/674x826/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/KARNIRXOS5GNDGE2VMNVRMATF4.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F2sBsHtiJ2LSLt1V0WCV4ILwOmi0%3D%2F674x826%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FKARNIRXOS5GNDGE2VMNVRMATF4.gif&h=ce3f7a8f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n祝安寧度過黑暗<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/fvqPzaUMs_xOKlVd6k-3FNTW9mE=/590x755/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/O4PUFL3D7RDMPAPTOAFSIBAMGY.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FfvqPzaUMs_xOKlVd6k-3FNTW9mE%3D%2F590x755%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FO4PUFL3D7RDMPAPTOAFSIBAMGY.gif&h=0c152137&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n上帝與你同在<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/Te9W7BEa3NGdVyzUlQfMlXgrFLA=/706x382/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/YPL4PJ2UFRDSHMXQBQ6ZCIHEQY.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FTe9W7BEa3NGdVyzUlQfMlXgrFLA%3D%2F706x382%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FYPL4PJ2UFRDSHMXQBQ6ZCIHEQY.gif&h=7a91269e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n當權者良心泯滅<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/eTCStllZEE44IbV3kTasteN34Ig=/701x478/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/L5ZJK3YSLZGVRA3PTJF6HCMI5U.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FeTCStllZEE44IbV3kTasteN34Ig%3D%2F701x478%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FL5ZJK3YSLZGVRA3PTJF6HCMI5U.gif&h=820f9249&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n香港人永遠在你身邊"},{"pid":"9c9d1407676d2fed21ad0098135c6f3c88d01e7c","tid":2311366,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-10T07:20:44.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201210/JCGDJBOGKNAK7J6S4HBTYLJAXI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201210%2FJCGDJBOGKNAK7J6S4HBTYLJAXI%2F&d=my%2BdBOIpGqNKE9iEaZHJGNWqQ%2Br5Wu6dnGlIIIMUdw0%3D&h=fb3cc008\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201210%2FJCGDJBOGKNAK7J6S4HBTYLJAXI%2F&h=bac902e3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201210/JCGDJBOGKNAK7J6S4HBTYLJAXI/</a><br />\n<br />\n你唔放棄HK人 我哋唔會放棄你<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/u-ZpWehYWNspftMw-zSCQ-Soc08=/1767x1181/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/AD4MS3QEXFBBDO3T7QRFT7R3TI.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fu-ZpWehYWNspftMw-zSCQ-Soc08%3D%2F1767x1181%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FAD4MS3QEXFBBDO3T7QRFT7R3TI.jpg&h=5b3a0ce2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■黎智英對讀者連日親筆來信表示感激。<br />\n<br />\n壹傳媒集團創辦人黎智英被控欺詐罪，遭關押荔枝角收押所至今一周，一眾老讀者、舊戰友，還有新相識的年輕人都堅持親筆來信，為他打氣加油。有教師洋洋六頁紙訴說百般滋味在心頭，並引聖經經文與黎智英共勉；有從前不理政治的新移民來信叫「肥佬」加油，一字一句都是繁體字，「就算沒有錢食飯，都要買蘋果日報」。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：黎智英本周復看《蘋果》：謝讀者祝福<br />\n今時今日，執筆提字的人很少，寫給「肥佬黎」的信卻很多。其中讀者C小姐親筆的一封信長達六頁紙，跟「肥佬」訴說感受。她說除了訂閱蘋果動新聞外，每天都會買一份《蘋果日報》，也看見有些黃店放滿了《蘋果日報》以示支持，「您的堅持實在令不少香港人動容，亦鼓勵我學習您的堅持」。<br />\n<br />\n除了C小姐，開宗明義「N年無拎筆之人」則寫了一封英文信給「肥佬黎」，老實不客氣指他在部份人眼中或許不是好人，但對所有真香港人而言，絕對是好人一個。她說，過去兩年生活過得不順，但對比起香港這個家所經歷的事，只是小事一樁，她會努力克服困難，所以「肥佬」都要好好保重。<br />\n<br />\n「200+1香港人」也說，良久沒提筆寫信予親人，感覺有點陌生，「相信夢中驚醒的，徹夜難眠的，寒夜醒來的非只有這一撮人」。他說三人行必有黃絲，寄語被扣押的「親人」，「只要內心無懼，自然強，腰板挺直，風骨正」，大事大非更要心境明淨。有讀者自言不懂大道理，「但我知乜嘢係良心、公義」，來信快人快語，「你唔放棄HK人，我哋都唔會放棄你，支持你，加油！」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/cATIJlfAnR8WVAa28jxReZvYPAQ=/1759x1181/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/7M4GYUBWGZD2VEOLQJQA7VTCQY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FcATIJlfAnR8WVAa28jxReZvYPAQ%3D%2F1759x1181%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F7M4GYUBWGZD2VEOLQJQA7VTCQY.jpg&h=283e77fc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■除親筆信外，有讀者更獻上畫作，着黎智英如壁虎般「撐實」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/CQmX8exShW4N1HRZxa97DFCz0Fk=/1174x1299/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/FOWDDTKX2JDFXLQSYEA5VC5PHI.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FCQmX8exShW4N1HRZxa97DFCz0Fk%3D%2F1174x1299%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FFOWDDTKX2JDFXLQSYEA5VC5PHI.gif&h=bd9612d6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n腰板挺直風骨正<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/WpxTBYUkuUY_-q-A0i578GJhlrs=/1435x1024/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/KVMC36NXAJEEVHH3XXVFLH5DQE.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FWpxTBYUkuUY_-q-A0i578GJhlrs%3D%2F1435x1024%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FKVMC36NXAJEEVHH3XXVFLH5DQE.gif&h=852b18dc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n黎明總有天會來<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/mfBUi2aqbRGRG8Up6KppyAjLG20=/1297x2034/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/325IFBMICZEH3IPQGA3TITVHO4.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FmfBUi2aqbRGRG8Up6KppyAjLG20%3D%2F1297x2034%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F325IFBMICZEH3IPQGA3TITVHO4.gif&h=aac70acc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n香港人以你為榮 盼有天與你相擁<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/XSSgnN0n78yn_c6-3COZ8y79igw=/944x1218/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/EH3FLR6QTZGCHCGBSHLDSNHIZQ.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FXSSgnN0n78yn_c6-3COZ8y79igw%3D%2F944x1218%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FEH3FLR6QTZGCHCGBSHLDSNHIZQ.gif&h=7db50a59&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n不畏強權 報道真相<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/MG4u5nYceHo64ADOpfl_6fhDka0=/1145x663/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/7CUJGIKYIVGNZD2O7YCZMXN72E.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FMG4u5nYceHo64ADOpfl_6fhDka0%3D%2F1145x663%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F7CUJGIKYIVGNZD2O7YCZMXN72E.gif&h=b8c4cfc0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n每日買實體報支持"},{"pid":"c299fc5df416ac889486c6909bc2a144fdfca3ed","tid":2311366,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-11T09:05:25.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201211/7X4PWV6IWFECBJ5NNRHNYRCMTY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201211%2F7X4PWV6IWFECBJ5NNRHNYRCMTY%2F&d=my%2BdBOIpGqNKE9iEaZHJGNWqQ%2Br5Wu6dnGlIIIMUdw0%3D&h=27da69ff\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201211%2F7X4PWV6IWFECBJ5NNRHNYRCMTY%2F&h=6645e370\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201211/7X4PWV6IWFECBJ5NNRHNYRCMTY/</a><br />\n<br />\n堅哥：我哋唔做契弟<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/Ma2sRTvN-_-tnpsdFo154231Coc=/1536x1024/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/55AWR4WAENBLTMYCHEKLAD6UWA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FMa2sRTvN-_-tnpsdFo154231Coc%3D%2F1536x1024%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F55AWR4WAENBLTMYCHEKLAD6UWA.jpg&h=9d8ea590&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n葉一堅<br />\n<br />\n上周被落案控以欺詐罪的壹傳媒創辦人黎智英，關押荔枝角收押所至今逾一周。有老臣子及市民堅持寫上一封封「給肥佬黎的信」，為鐵窗內的黎智英送暖。與黎智英並肩作戰20年的壹傳媒非執行董事葉一堅，以「阿Dee」為下款談起昔日點滴，說黎智英過去多年說了很多次，「挑，賣《蘋果》？移民？我唔X想做契弟喎！」有讀者形容黎為小飛俠（Peter Pan），「永遠都有個小孩住進了心裏。亦常常追隨你的信念和熱情，面對逆境」。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：黎智英：神畀嘅十字架欣然接受<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/Sw-w19BUMayYuYQwHjTaH_Ki1T4=/5041x2377/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/LKR7KB3NCZE6JBPNJ5ZEITZT5Y.GIF\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FSw-w19BUMayYuYQwHjTaH_Ki1T4%3D%2F5041x2377%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FLKR7KB3NCZE6JBPNJ5ZEITZT5Y.GIF&h=c34d6a54&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"211fa1e8ef3e3c18a9129129fb9c1487dc103829","tid":2311366,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-13T02:41:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nU3AGod.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnU3AGod.jpg&h=d9313425&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"504f312bf206e52afe7b768d30b56f86fe3dbcb6","tid":2311366,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-13T10:43:55.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201213/IBS6NSJXV5CLFG7R5S77ONQ72Y/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201213%2FIBS6NSJXV5CLFG7R5S77ONQ72Y%2F&d=my%2BdBOIpGqNKE9iEaZHJGNWqQ%2Br5Wu6dnGlIIIMUdw0%3D&h=bd46468e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201213%2FIBS6NSJXV5CLFG7R5S77ONQ72Y%2F&h=cac23c53\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201213/IBS6NSJXV5CLFG7R5S77ONQ72Y/</a><br />\n<br />\n「感謝您為下一代，留下承受一切」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/wdfjd2Y2K9Uxod_Io_8OilBEb6Y=/1000x563/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/OV7B3C23RJEBNOENSCQ65VN7D4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fwdfjd2Y2K9Uxod_Io_8OilBEb6Y%3D%2F1000x563%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FOV7B3C23RJEBNOENSCQ65VN7D4.jpg&h=1bf9d6c5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n我一定會守護這裏<br />\n<br />\n【讀者打氣】給黎智英的信繼續寄到本報，來信人為暫時無法張聲的「肥佬黎」申冤，也為香港一代傳媒大亨感到自豪。有女孩傳來親筆信，說一定要守護香港；有女士憑畫寄意，感謝他為這個家的付出。「感謝您一直以來為這個家的付出，為了香港的下一代，您選擇留下來承受這一切。」署名「香港讀者」的一位女子送上一幅由她繪畫的黎智英肖像，感謝他「在黑暗時刻仍堅持為香港燃點起這點光」。親筆信還有來自一位就讀小六的女學生，署名為「永遠愛香港的人，穿着黃衣的女孩」，信中畫了一名小女孩，她感謝黎智英盡心報道真相，她父母每天看新聞都非常生氣，「我不明白為甚麼政府對我們那麼壞，我們沒有做壞事吧！」儘管所有人都放棄香港，但她「一定會守護這裏的」。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：陸委會轟除異己「港將走向煉獄」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n香港美麗因為有您<br />\n<br />\n黎生：<br />\n<br />\n感謝您一直以來為這個家的付出，<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：歐美聲援 彭斯促放政治犯： 控黎等於侮辱愛自由的人<br />\n<br />\n為了香港的下一代，您選擇留下來承受這一切。<br />\n<br />\n在黑暗時刻仍然堅持為香港燃點起這點光。<br />\n<br />\n香港之所以美麗，因為有您和一眾堅守家園的香港人。<br />\n<br />\n請保重。<br />\n<br />\n香港讀者上<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/ITUFTdKocemj6c6WxFfLfafseyo=/886x1181/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/MACANT66FRD5XEUEJ4VUQY2WTY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FITUFTdKocemj6c6WxFfLfafseyo%3D%2F886x1181%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FMACANT66FRD5XEUEJ4VUQY2WTY.jpg&h=4fec60f2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/G270uZG09FXAidIfULCtvuhT0Ho=/1261x886/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/MNIMR2UQSNCGJGZGYD4OQLU2GA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FG270uZG09FXAidIfULCtvuhT0Ho%3D%2F1261x886%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FMNIMR2UQSNCGJGZGYD4OQLU2GA.jpg&h=ebf5b517&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n謝謝你的付出<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/TwUt-VR9O2iIpdgtjPY7rGr7y3c=/1304x886/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/TTIVEAAJGJAF3A2JNKQOY4OYM4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FTwUt-VR9O2iIpdgtjPY7rGr7y3c%3D%2F1304x886%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FTTIVEAAJGJAF3A2JNKQOY4OYM4.jpg&h=2d1ff627&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■5歲小朋友Erin親手繪製聖誕卡為黎智英打氣，祝福他身體健康，早日重獲自由。"},{"pid":"77ca796182b5a21fc59fdea12a2512bbecb25be1","tid":2311366,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-14T10:17:24.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201214/22GHYIDFPJEHDJU2245Z5SZXUE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201214%2F22GHYIDFPJEHDJU2245Z5SZXUE%2F&d=my%2BdBOIpGqNKE9iEaZHJGNWqQ%2Br5Wu6dnGlIIIMUdw0%3D&h=ac8f6e00\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201214%2F22GHYIDFPJEHDJU2245Z5SZXUE%2F&h=472b67ce\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201214/22GHYIDFPJEHDJU2245Z5SZXUE/</a><br />\n<br />\n不要害怕 有我協助你<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/FYUhJbiaAXiGoZ3uEDryccCKUWs=/2126x1476/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/XPUFVJ7FSNAEVA3Y5J7EXKUYME.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FFYUhJbiaAXiGoZ3uEDryccCKUWs%3D%2F2126x1476%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FXPUFVJ7FSNAEVA3Y5J7EXKUYME.jpg&h=12d456da&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■讀者以畫像記錄黎腰纏鐵鏈、雙手鎖上手銬一幕，並配上《若望福音》的經文勉勵。<br />\n<br />\n極權以惡法生效前的證據檢控壹傳媒創辦人黎智英，激起每一位有良知香港人的怒火，多位讀者來函支持。有讀者直言看到黎被鎖上手銬押上囚車，感到非常難受，引用《聖經》經文&mdash;&mdash;因為是我，上主，你的天主，提攜著你的右手，向你說過：「不要害怕，有我協助你。」（依41:13），勉勵黎有主同在，縱然面對壓迫和枷鎖，但內心的自由是不能被壓迫和暴力奪去。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：台外長推文「讓香港自由」<br />\n<br />\n有讀者則留意到黎智英在庭上向旁聽者做心心手勢，感謝他仍盡力讓大家放心，又以二戰時邪惡政權自信可統治世界為喻，深信極權終將敗陣。<br />\n<br />\n讀者以不同方法為黎智英加油，有海外華人讀者即使有三個《蘋果》賬戶，昨再參加了《蘋果》VIP會員計劃，感謝黎的勇敢堅毅激發了港人的潛能和理想，並相信反送中種子將培育出不可預計的大變局，願與黎共見此天。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：WSJ：他的罪名是批評北京<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n堅持講真話<br />\n<br />\n黎智英先生：<br />\n<br />\n由中學開始我已經閱讀《蘋果日報》，是《蘋果》的報道讓我學習關心香港。感謝你一直苦心經營，在其他傳媒因壓力或利益選擇自我審查和歸邊時， 《蘋果日報》卻堅持講真話，在黑暗的環境下仍然堅持發光，堅守新聞價值。<br />\n<br />\n看到你被鎖上手銬押上囚車，感到非常難受。但你的平靜卻為我們香港人立了很好的榜樣，縱然面對外在的壓迫和枷鎖，你仍然能夠保持內心的自由。這種自由是任何壓迫和暴力都不能奪去的。<br />\n<br />\n聖經說:「因為是我，上主，你的天主，提攜著你的右手，向你說過：「不要害怕，有我協助你。」(依41:13) 無論如何，請信靠仁慈的天主，祂在任何處境中都會與你同在。期待你自由之日！為你祈禱！<br />\n<br />\nFrancis<br />\n<br />\nEvery cloud has a silver lining<br />\nJimmy,<br />\n<br />\n香港傀儡政權砌詞將你加控勾結外國勢力的罪名，本該令人擔心和憤慨，因為這會增加你受到牢獄之災的機會。但從另一方面看，你的犧牲已引起全球媒體的報道和各國的關注。再一次將中國共產黨的醜陋面目清楚展示給所有人看見。證明外國政府制裁中國及停止遣返逃犯到香港的協議是絕對正確的，更進一步促使他們放寬收容香港人的政策。這是共黨拿起石頭來砸自己的腳的明證。<br />\n<br />\n再者，因為你這樣不畏死，彰顯民主的精神，一洗最初對你人格有懷疑者的看法。這種殉道的行徑也加強了支持者對你的尊重。<br />\n<br />\n請照顧好自己的身體。<br />\n<br />\n保持希望，every cloud has a silver lining !<br />\n<br />\n願上主保護你<br />\n<br />\nMagda<br />\n<br />\n以意志掙斷鐵鏈<br />\n敬愛的黎先生：<br />\n<br />\n讀報知悉你昨天在庭上對旁聽者做心心手勢，很想感謝你在這個時候仍然盡力叫我們放心。你的心意，我們都收到了。<br />\n<br />\n昨天故意要羞辱你的，真是可笑。對於他們用上鐵鏈固然心痛，可是我看到的，是被你的風骨、意志快要掙斷四散的鐵鏈。我們就一起堅強下去，反正二戰時候自信可以統治世界的邪惡，最後還不是抱頭敗走嗎？<br />\n<br />\n天氣涼了，若覺得外衣不夠暖，請務必提出啊。<br />\n<br />\n掛念你的手足上"},{"pid":"1bef2ed66d70b03923e29fd5a4ab4dc4e89df64a","tid":2311366,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-15T03:22:55.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201215/7W2ZQDSUS5E4TG5TKXDPMKLOJY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201215%2F7W2ZQDSUS5E4TG5TKXDPMKLOJY%2F&d=my%2BdBOIpGqNKE9iEaZHJGNWqQ%2Br5Wu6dnGlIIIMUdw0%3D&h=1423c798\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201215%2F7W2ZQDSUS5E4TG5TKXDPMKLOJY%2F&h=a5ff6393\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201215/7W2ZQDSUS5E4TG5TKXDPMKLOJY/</a><br />\n<br />\n《蘋果》一定撐落去 關關難過關關過<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/j_VXGAZ7vVsJj6DFfRKRGghTmF0=/988x740/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/WRWXPNOSHJCHXKV2RDTL5FS5HE.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fj_VXGAZ7vVsJj6DFfRKRGghTmF0%3D%2F988x740%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FWRWXPNOSHJCHXKV2RDTL5FS5HE.gif&h=8262576e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■有讀者提前送來聖誕卡，希望黎智英早日獲批保釋。<br />\n<br />\n極權用盡辦法掩藏和打壓真相，卻無減真相價值半分。多位讀者來函支持壹傳媒創辦人黎智英，更有人提前送來聖誕賀卡，希望他早日獲准保釋。一名「見閻王前一秒也要看蘋果日報」的讀者親筆來信，寫滿四頁紙。他讚揚黎智英不舔共，選擇為快要沉淪的香港大聲呼疾，辦報堅守言論陣地，抗擊黨報顛倒是非，即使面對中共以「拉人封報」攻勢封殺，黎亦未有懼色。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：下周三申保釋 國安官負責<br />\n<br />\n有小讀者來函憶起8.11「蘋果圍戰」，想起黎生「《蘋果》一定撐落去！」的豪言。有讀者形容2020年香港動盪不安，眼見黎智英被捕，日後可能波及更多記者，「我們只可眼白白地見證着，不知又有多少手足面臨鐵柵之苦，不知極權何時完結，不知香港重現光明的時候」。但她鼓勵同路人，就算要頭破血流，都要拚命做下去，「難以在香港撼動極權政府，便跳出香港，讓全世界知道，永留青史。就算危機四伏，關關難過關關過，在自己份內盡力而為，對嗎？」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/bt7DICLrgAI6fEagHjkLqnhyclk=/1481x2067/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/JZKJDBSYT5HPVOFEY2YE24IKH4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fbt7DICLrgAI6fEagHjkLqnhyclk%3D%2F1481x2067%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FJZKJDBSYT5HPVOFEY2YE24IKH4.jpg&h=629ee8eb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n你不會孤軍作戰<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/grlAugFIDnNBKz8ltI86oTCb4-g=/1275x1772/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/MHHRPISNUNEJPNSYYUTXEUGZK4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FgrlAugFIDnNBKz8ltI86oTCb4-g%3D%2F1275x1772%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FMHHRPISNUNEJPNSYYUTXEUGZK4.jpg&h=7da64d4b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n面對極權 毫不畏懼"},{"pid":"406754a2cb5620d42fb602b5f5ea95373deb5edd","tid":2311366,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-21T14:53:58.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201221/EBC43HQZHJDMVNKMV7KZUAQUIU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201221%2FEBC43HQZHJDMVNKMV7KZUAQUIU%2F&d=my%2BdBOIpGqNKE9iEaZHJGNWqQ%2Br5Wu6dnGlIIIMUdw0%3D&h=a9359cc0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201221%2FEBC43HQZHJDMVNKMV7KZUAQUIU%2F&h=423fc09f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201221/EBC43HQZHJDMVNKMV7KZUAQUIU/</a><br />\n<br />\n「今生只想和你合影一張」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/fVa7HSd1tIwf1L6Hk8bfroO0DGg=/842x493/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/CFEDUOW2QBFWLJQXQTX3N5OPP4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FfVa7HSd1tIwf1L6Hk8bfroO0DGg%3D%2F842x493%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FCFEDUOW2QBFWLJQXQTX3N5OPP4.png&h=e6b1eb13&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■黎智英至今被關押19天。<br />\n<br />\n【讀者打氣】<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：台學者轟北京廢立會「港陷戒嚴時代」 籲台擔當關鍵角色施援<br />\n<br />\n壹傳媒創辦人黎智英至今已被關押19天，港人堅持與他並肩同行。<br />\n<br />\n有讀者表示因為黎入獄失眠了好幾天，鼓勵「黎伯伯要堅持及振作，全香港、全世界有良知的人，是等着你回來的」。<br />\n<br />\n讀者Cathy來信，訴說眼見香港再無言論自由，心情很灰，她透露去年曾在警署被拘留24小時，明白失去自由、度日如年的感受，令她更了解寫信予在囚手足的重要性，雖然黎託人帶口信說在入面一切如常，「但實質咩情況我點會唔知」。<br />\n<br />\n她稱之前試過在旺角警署離遠看見黎，但因太多記者，結果只能看到黎的頭髮，「今生只想和你合影一張」。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n相信有天等到無罪釋放<br />\n<br />\n現在每天早上就是在搜尋器上搜尋你的名字，看看有沒有你的最新消息。我和所有真正香港人都相信有天會等到你被無罪釋放嘅好消息。要努力支持下去。<br />\n<br />\nProud of you<br />\n<br />\n十分以你為榮的香港人上<br />\n<br />\n更努力守護我們的家<br />\n敬愛的黎先生：<br />\n<br />\n今天天氣寒冷。你還好嗎？夠衣裳穿嗎？<br />\n<br />\n早前收到《壹週刊》告知大家關於出版月曆事宜，我第一時間到同路人商店購買五份。今天收到了。你可以放心，設計與實物都並非像其他隨便送人級數。謝謝你們的用心。我和家人都會放在枱頭，為自己打氣之餘，更努力守護我們的家。<br />\n<br />\n這一個充滿愛、充滿自主、思想自由、任何破壞者都不會得逞的家。<br />\n<br />\n掛念你的手足上<br />\n<br />\nTo strive, to seek, to find, and not to yield<br />\nOur salute to your ardent support of democracy for Hong Kong. You are a true Stoic of the 21st century.<br />\n<br />\nThe Hong Kong people are galvanized by your suffering and we are praying for your early release everyday.<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;Adversity breeds strength&rdquo;......We are many, they are few......To strive, to seek, to find, and not to yield.<br />\n<br />\nWishing you and your family many blessed years to come.<br />\n<br />\nElizabeth<br />\n<br />\n政權越羞辱越顯虛偽<br />\n黎先生，今日港共政權越對你百般羞辱，越顯得（牠們）虛偽，只會令港人及西方民主國家對你更尊重，（牠們）嘅偽善只會跟民主及法治潮流越走越遠，有良知香港人一定會與你並肩而行， 永不言敗， 祝你同家人一切安好，保重身體為上。<br />\n<br />\n一個黃到金的香港人敬上<br />\n<br />\n唔想齋寫一句手足加油就算<br />\n一個普通香港人，33歲女子。眼見香港再無言論自由，心情好灰。再見到你為香港人受嘅苦，更加無力。<br />\n<br />\n普通香港人好難發聲，見到你無辜入獄，一個香港人又能為你做到甚麼。今日只想到想為你寫封信。寫一封好普通嘅信。我不知信的內容是否寫幾多你就睇到幾多，其實有無限字數。亦都不知道你睇不睇到。<br />\n<br />\n上年我喺差館都拘留咗24個鐘，明白無自由嘅感受。 體驗到度秒如年嘅感受。同佢哋嘅飯盒實在食唔到，太難食了。嗰次24小時內我只飲咗三杯水同咬咗一啖三文治。瞓唔夠三個鐘，當時同外界完全斷絕嘅感覺，所以更令我明白到寫信畀囚中手足睇嘅重要性。我唔想齋寫一句手足加油就算，我想你可以睇耐啲封信，所以我之後會寫下我普通香港人一日嘅無聊嘢畀你睇。我亦都知用電郵（貪方便）寫有咁好，用親筆寫比較好，你可以感受到每一行字嘅變化，冇咁死咕咕。<br />\n<br />\n2020年我開始寫日記，記錄下每日發生嘅事，因每日嘅事我都覺得好震撼。黃色經濟圈喺我心目中開始強大了，有時心情差，會特登去下黃店，偷偷見下同路人。見到仲有咁多手足，心情就會好。真的，黎生希望你可以放返出來，不想你受苦。雖然你常託人帶口信你喺入面一切如常，但實則咩情況我點會唔知。我之前喺旺角差館遠處有來看你，不過太多記者了，只看到你頭髮幾秒，笑。今生只想和你合影一張，之前又點會接觸到你大人物。寫住咁多先，下次再寫。因我真的不知你究竟係咪真係睇到我封信，無奈笑。<br />\n<br />\n有一個問題想問好耐，就係支持蘋果日報究竟係支持畀錢訂閱實際啲，定係支持每日實體蘋果報好啲？聽人講支持訂閱好，但又怕俾人唱蘋果日報每日出報份數越來越少。最後黎生，聽人講用爽身粉摻喺床上易瞓，你叫家人入下畀你嘗試下。撐住吖，黎生。"}]}